    "The output of a virtual try-on system is an image m g, in which the human body p t is shown wearing the target clothes c t and the body shape and pose of the model in the input image are preserved.",
    "Semantic information about the clothing and models is also fed into the system as one kind of supervision information.",
    "A basic virtual try-on framework is illustrated in Fig. 8.",
    "In order to simplify the problem, the backgrounds of the clothing and human body images are usually clear.",
    "In a fashion shop, image pairs, i.e., a model wearing the clothes in the target image, are easy to obtain."
  ],
